{
  "video_id": "_bphPa7Wp4c",
  "title": "This tiny particle could roam your body to find tumors | Sangeeta Bhatia",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12557.0,
      "end_time": 16235.0,
      "text": "In the space that used to house one transistor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16259.0,
      "end_time": 19980.0,
      "text": "we can now fit one billion."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19636.0,
      "end_time": 23532.0,
      "text": "That made it so that a computer the size of an entire room"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 23557.0,
      "end_time": 26145.0,
      "text": "now fits in your pocket."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 26170.0,
      "end_time": 29189.0,
      "text": "You might say the future is small."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 29611.0,
      "end_time": 30818.0,
      "text": "As an engineer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 30842.0,
      "end_time": 34827.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m inspired by this miniaturization revolution in computers."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 34851.0,
      "end_time": 36199.0,
      "text": "As a physician,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 36223.0,
      "end_time": 41946.0,
      "text": "I wonder whether we could use it to reduce the number of lives lost"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 41970.0,
      "end_time": 46770.0,
      "text": "due to one of the fastest-growing diseases on Earth:"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 46101.0,
      "end_time": 47519.0,
      "text": "cancer."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 47543.0,
      "end_time": 48798.0,
      "text": "Now when I say that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 48822.0,
      "end_time": 52600.0,
      "text": "what most people hear me say is that we&#39;re working on curing cancer."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 52624.0,
      "end_time": 53887.0,
      "text": "And we are."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 53911.0,
      "end_time": 55620.0,
      "text": "But it turns out"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 55860.0,
      "end_time": 57887.0,
      "text": "that there&#39;s an incredible opportunity to save lives"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 57911.0,
      "end_time": 61244.0,
      "text": "through the early detection and prevention of cancer."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 61785.0,
      "end_time": 67164.0,
      "text": "Worldwide, over two-thirds of deaths due to cancer are fully preventable"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 67188.0,
      "end_time": 69988.0,
      "text": "using methods that we already have in hand today."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 70406.0,
      "end_time": 73305.0,
      "text": "Things like vaccination, timely screening"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 73329.0,
      "end_time": 75562.0,
      "text": "and of course, stopping smoking."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 76316.0,
      "end_time": 79909.0,
      "text": "But even with the best tools and technologies that we have today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 79933.0,
      "end_time": 81996.0,
      "text": "some tumors can&#39;t be detected"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 82200.0,
      "end_time": 85690.0,
      "text": "until 10 years after they&#39;ve started growing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 85714.0,
      "end_time": 89477.0,
      "text": "when they are 50 million cancer cells strong."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 90178.0,
      "end_time": 91857.0,
      "text": "What if we had better technologies"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 91881.0,
      "end_time": 94987.0,
      "text": "to detect some of these more deadly cancers sooner,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 95110.0,
      "end_time": 96313.0,
      "text": "when they could be removed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 96337.0,
      "end_time": 98538.0,
      "text": "when they were just getting started?"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 98562.0,
      "end_time": 101837.0,
      "text": "Let me tell you about how miniaturization might get us there."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 103140.0,
      "end_time": 105428.0,
      "text": "This is a microscope in a typical lab"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 105452.0,
      "end_time": 109800.0,
      "text": "that a pathologist would use for looking at a tissue specimen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 109320.0,
      "end_time": 111470.0,
      "text": "like a biopsy or a pap smear."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 111927.0,
      "end_time": 113995.0,
      "text": "This $7,000 microscope"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 114190.0,
      "end_time": 117275.0,
      "text": "would be used by somebody with years of specialized training"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 117299.0,
      "end_time": 119880.0,
      "text": "to spot cancer cells."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 120126.0,
      "end_time": 123172.0,
      "text": "This is an image from a colleague of mine at Rice University,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 123196.0,
      "end_time": 124774.0,
      "text": "Rebecca Richards-Kortum."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 124798.0,
      "end_time": 128625.0,
      "text": "What she and her team have done is miniaturize that whole microscope"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 128649.0,
      "end_time": 130624.0,
      "text": "into this $10 part,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 130648.0,
      "end_time": 133464.0,
      "text": "and it fits on the end of an optical fiber."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 133923.0,
      "end_time": 137557.0,
      "text": "Now what that means is instead of taking a sample from a patient"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 137581.0,
      "end_time": 139230.0,
      "text": "and sending it to the microscope,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 139254.0,
      "end_time": 141810.0,
      "text": "you can bring the microscope to the patient."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 142260.0,
      "end_time": 146619.0,
      "text": "And then, instead of requiring a specialist to look at the images,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 146643.0,
      "end_time": 151705.0,
      "text": "you can train the computer to score normal versus cancerous cells."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 152840.0,
      "end_time": 153254.0,
      "text": "Now this is important,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 153278.0,
      "end_time": 156315.0,
      "text": "because what they found working in rural communities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 156339.0,
      "end_time": 159578.0,
      "text": "is that even when they have a mobile screening van"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 159602.0,
      "end_time": 162435.0,
      "text": "that can go out into the community and perform exams"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 162459.0,
      "end_time": 163864.0,
      "text": "and collect samples"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 163888.0,
      "end_time": 167104.0,
      "text": "and send them to the central hospital for analysis,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 167128.0,
      "end_time": 168471.0,
      "text": "that days later,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 168496.0,
      "end_time": 171163.0,
      "text": "women get a call with an abnormal test result"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 171187.0,
      "end_time": 172804.0,
      "text": "and they&#39;re asked to come in."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 172828.0,
      "end_time": 177171.0,
      "text": "Fully half of them don&#39;t turn up because they can&#39;t afford the trip."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 177721.0,
      "end_time": 181145.0,
      "text": "With the integrated microscope and computer analysis,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 181169.0,
      "end_time": 183997.0,
      "text": "Rebecca and her colleagues have been able to create a van"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 184210.0,
      "end_time": 187807.0,
      "text": "that has both a diagnostic setup and a treatment setup."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 187831.0,
      "end_time": 190545.0,
      "text": "And what that means is that they can do a diagnosis"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 190569.0,
      "end_time": 193256.0,
      "text": "and perform therapy on the spot,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 193280.0,
      "end_time": 195418.0,
      "text": "so no one is lost to follow up."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 195831.0,
      "end_time": 199779.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s just one example of how miniaturization can save lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 200148.0,
      "end_time": 201301.0,
      "text": "Now as engineers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 201325.0,
      "end_time": 204700.0,
      "text": "we think of this as straight-up miniaturization."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 204940.0,
      "end_time": 206531.0,
      "text": "You took a big thing and you made it little."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 206555.0,
      "end_time": 208806.0,
      "text": "But what I told you before about computers"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 208830.0,
      "end_time": 211760.0,
      "text": "was that they transformed our lives"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 211100.0,
      "end_time": 215400.0,
      "text": "when they became small enough for us to take them everywhere."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 215785.0,
      "end_time": 220810.0,
      "text": "So what is the transformational equivalent like that in medicine?"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 220500.0,
      "end_time": 223636.0,
      "text": "Well, what if you had a detector"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 223660.0,
      "end_time": 227922.0,
      "text": "that was so small that it could circulate in your body,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 227946.0,
      "end_time": 230359.0,
      "text": "find the tumor all by itself"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 230383.0,
      "end_time": 232752.0,
      "text": "and send a signal to the outside world?"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 233790.0,
      "end_time": 235156.0,
      "text": "It sounds a little bit like science fiction."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 235180.0,
      "end_time": 239830.0,
      "text": "But actually, nanotechnology allows us to do just that."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 239415.0,
      "end_time": 244296.0,
      "text": "Nanotechnology allows us to shrink the parts that make up the detector"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 244320.0,
      "end_time": 246156.0,
      "text": "from the width of a human hair,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 246181.0,
      "end_time": 247841.0,
      "text": "which is 100 microns,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 247865.0,
      "end_time": 250420.0,
      "text": "to a thousand times smaller,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 250444.0,
      "end_time": 252345.0,
      "text": "which is 100 nanometers."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 252370.0,
      "end_time": 255180.0,
      "text": "And that has profound implications."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 255583.0,
      "end_time": 259226.0,
      "text": "It turns out that materials actually change their properties"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 259250.0,
      "end_time": 260846.0,
      "text": "at the nanoscale."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 261279.0,
      "end_time": 263777.0,
      "text": "You take a common material like gold,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 263801.0,
      "end_time": 267122.0,
      "text": "and you grind it into dust, into gold nanoparticles,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 267146.0,
      "end_time": 270458.0,
      "text": "and it changes from looking gold to looking red."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 271820.0,
      "end_time": 274895.0,
      "text": "If you take a more exotic material like cadmium selenide --"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 274919.0,
      "end_time": 277920.0,
      "text": "forms a big, black crystal --"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 277117.0,
      "end_time": 279718.0,
      "text": "if you make nanocrystals out of this material"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 279742.0,
      "end_time": 281315.0,
      "text": "and you put it in a liquid,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 281339.0,
      "end_time": 283163.0,
      "text": "and you shine light on it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 283187.0,
      "end_time": 284353.0,
      "text": "they glow."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 284377.0,
      "end_time": 290800.0,
      "text": "And they glow blue, green, yellow, orange, red,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 290320.0,
      "end_time": 292306.0,
      "text": "depending only on their size."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 292887.0,
      "end_time": 296890.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s wild! Can you imagine an object like that in the macro world?"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 296914.0,
      "end_time": 303485.0,
      "text": "It would be like all the denim jeans in your closet are all made of cotton,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 303509.0,
      "end_time": 307820.0,
      "text": "but they are different colors depending only on their size."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 308212.0,
      "end_time": 309908.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 310982.0,
      "end_time": 312506.0,
      "text": "So as a physician,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 312530.0,
      "end_time": 314753.0,
      "text": "what&#39;s just as interesting to me"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 314778.0,
      "end_time": 317780.0,
      "text": "is that it&#39;s not just the color of materials"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 317102.0,
      "end_time": 319320.0,
      "text": "that changes at the nanoscale;"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 319570.0,
      "end_time": 322665.0,
      "text": "the way they travel in your body also changes."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 323137.0,
      "end_time": 325936.0,
      "text": "And this is the kind of observation that we&#39;re going to use"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 325960.0,
      "end_time": 328133.0,
      "text": "to make a better cancer detector."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 328158.0,
      "end_time": 329911.0,
      "text": "So let me show you what I mean."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 330686.0,
      "end_time": 332883.0,
      "text": "This is a blood vessel in the body."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 332907.0,
      "end_time": 335318.0,
      "text": "Surrounding the blood vessel is a tumor."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 335683.0,
      "end_time": 338724.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re going to inject nanoparticles into the blood vessel"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 338748.0,
      "end_time": 342928.0,
      "text": "and watch how they travel from the bloodstream into the tumor."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 343464.0,
      "end_time": 347816.0,
      "text": "Now it turns out that the blood vessels of many tumors are leaky,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 347840.0,
      "end_time": 352205.0,
      "text": "and so nanoparticles can leak out from the bloodstream into the tumor."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 352628.0,
      "end_time": 355762.0,
      "text": "Whether they leak out depends on their size."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 356129.0,
      "end_time": 357279.0,
      "text": "So in this image,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 357303.0,
      "end_time": 361674.0,
      "text": "the smaller, hundred-nanometer, blue nanoparticles are leaking out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 361698.0,
      "end_time": 365940.0,
      "text": "and the larger, 500-nanometer, red nanoparticles"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 365118.0,
      "end_time": 366895.0,
      "text": "are stuck in the bloodstream."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 366919.0,
      "end_time": 369220.0,
      "text": "So that means as an engineer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 369460.0,
      "end_time": 373380.0,
      "text": "depending on how big or small I make a material,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 373620.0,
      "end_time": 376103.0,
      "text": "I can change where it goes in your body."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 377249.0,
      "end_time": 381891.0,
      "text": "In my lab, we recently made a cancer nanodetector"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 381915.0,
      "end_time": 387163.0,
      "text": "that is so small that it could travel into the body and look for tumors."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 387477.0,
      "end_time": 391568.0,
      "text": "We designed it to listen for tumor invasion:"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 391593.0,
      "end_time": 396366.0,
      "text": "the orchestra of chemical signals that tumors need to make to spread."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 396932.0,
      "end_time": 399834.0,
      "text": "For a tumor to break out of the tissue that it&#39;s born in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 399858.0,
      "end_time": 402574.0,
      "text": "it has to make chemicals called enzymes"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 402598.0,
      "end_time": 405182.0,
      "text": "to chew through the scaffolding of tissues."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 405763.0,
      "end_time": 410484.0,
      "text": "We designed these nanoparticles to be activated by these enzymes."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 411340.0,
      "end_time": 416945.0,
      "text": "One enzyme can activate a thousand of these chemical reactions in an hour."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 417462.0,
      "end_time": 421200.0,
      "text": "Now in engineering, we call that one-to-a-thousand ratio"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 421440.0,
      "end_time": 422609.0,
      "text": "a form of amplification,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 422633.0,
      "end_time": 424805.0,
      "text": "and it makes something ultrasensitive."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 424829.0,
      "end_time": 428662.0,
      "text": "So we&#39;ve made an ultrasensitive cancer detector."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 429220.0,
      "end_time": 434120.0,
      "text": "OK, but how do I get this activated signal to the outside world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 434144.0,
      "end_time": 435882.0,
      "text": "where I can act on it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 435906.0,
      "end_time": 439458.0,
      "text": "For this, we&#39;re going to use one more piece of nanoscale biology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 439482.0,
      "end_time": 441266.0,
      "text": "and that has to do with the kidney."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 441659.0,
      "end_time": 443575.0,
      "text": "The kidney is a filter."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 443996.0,
      "end_time": 448625.0,
      "text": "Its job is to filter out the blood and put waste into the urine."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 449197.0,
      "end_time": 451859.0,
      "text": "It turns out that what the kidney filters"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 451883.0,
      "end_time": 454445.0,
      "text": "is also dependent on size."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 454901.0,
      "end_time": 456841.0,
      "text": "So in this image, what you can see"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 456865.0,
      "end_time": 459874.0,
      "text": "is that everything smaller than five nanometers"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 459898.0,
      "end_time": 464300.0,
      "text": "is going from the blood, through the kidney, into the urine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 464270.0,
      "end_time": 466697.0,
      "text": "and everything else that&#39;s bigger is retained."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 467176.0,
      "end_time": 472123.0,
      "text": "OK, so if I make a 100-nanometer cancer detector,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 472147.0,
      "end_time": 474619.0,
      "text": "I inject it in the bloodstream,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 474643.0,
      "end_time": 480730.0,
      "text": "it can leak into the tumor where it&#39;s activated by tumor enzymes"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 480970.0,
      "end_time": 482453.0,
      "text": "to release a small signal"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 482477.0,
      "end_time": 485698.0,
      "text": "that is small enough to be filtered out of the kidney"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 485723.0,
      "end_time": 487901.0,
      "text": "and put into the urine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 487925.0,
      "end_time": 491966.0,
      "text": "I have a signal in the outside world that I can detect."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 492588.0,
      "end_time": 494640.0,
      "text": "OK, but there&#39;s one more problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 494664.0,
      "end_time": 496409.0,
      "text": "This is a tiny little signal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 496434.0,
      "end_time": 498406.0,
      "text": "so how do I detect it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 498730.0,
      "end_time": 500965.0,
      "text": "Well, the signal is just a molecule."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 500989.0,
      "end_time": 503655.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re molecules that we designed as engineers."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 503680.0,
      "end_time": 506858.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re completely synthetic, and we can design them"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 506882.0,
      "end_time": 510121.0,
      "text": "so they are compatible with our tool of choice."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 510145.0,
      "end_time": 513587.0,
      "text": "If we want to use a really sensitive, fancy instrument"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 513611.0,
      "end_time": 515575.0,
      "text": "called a mass spectrometer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 515599.00000000006,
      "end_time": 518110.00000000006,
      "text": "then we make a molecule with a unique mass."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 518671.00000000006,
      "end_time": 522370.00000000006,
      "text": "Or maybe we want make something that&#39;s more inexpensive and portable."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 522394.0,
      "end_time": 526177.0,
      "text": "Then we make molecules that we can trap on paper,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 526201.0,
      "end_time": 527905.0,
      "text": "like a pregnancy test."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 527929.0,
      "end_time": 530555.0,
      "text": "In fact, there&#39;s a whole world of paper tests"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 530579.0,
      "end_time": 535900.0,
      "text": "that are becoming available in a field called paper diagnostics."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 535711.0,
      "end_time": 538370.0,
      "text": "Alright, where are we going with this?"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 538724.0,
      "end_time": 540293.0,
      "text": "What I&#39;m going to tell you next,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 540317.0,
      "end_time": 542143.0,
      "text": "as a lifelong researcher,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 542167.0,
      "end_time": 544460.0,
      "text": "represents a dream of mine."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 544396.0,
      "end_time": 546488.0,
      "text": "I can&#39;t say that&#39;s it&#39;s a promise;"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 546513.0,
      "end_time": 548500.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s a dream."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 548290.0,
      "end_time": 551616.0,
      "text": "But I think we all have to have dreams to keep us pushing forward,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 551640.0,
      "end_time": 555577.0,
      "text": "even -- and maybe especially -- cancer researchers."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 555601.0,
      "end_time": 559100.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m going to tell you what I hope will happen with my technology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 559124.0,
      "end_time": 563215.0,
      "text": "that my team and I will put our hearts and souls"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 563239.0,
      "end_time": 564761.0,
      "text": "into making a reality."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 565289.0,
      "end_time": 566987.0,
      "text": "OK, here goes."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 567110.0,
      "end_time": 570366.0,
      "text": "I dream that one day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 570390.0,
      "end_time": 573645.0,
      "text": "instead of going into an expensive screening facility"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 573669.0,
      "end_time": 575174.0,
      "text": "to get a colonoscopy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 575198.0,
      "end_time": 576521.0,
      "text": "or a mammogram,"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 576545.0,
      "end_time": 577953.0,
      "text": "or a pap smear,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 578585.0,
      "end_time": 580304.0,
      "text": "that you could get a shot,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 580328.0,
      "end_time": 581988.0,
      "text": "wait an hour,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 582120.0,
      "end_time": 584806.0,
      "text": "and do a urine test on a paper strip."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 585653.0,
      "end_time": 588460.0,
      "text": "I imagine that this could even happen"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 588484.0,
      "end_time": 591147.0,
      "text": "without the need for steady electricity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 591171.0,
      "end_time": 593775.0,
      "text": "or a medical professional in the room."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 593799.0,
      "end_time": 595295.0,
      "text": "Maybe they could be far away"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 595320.0,
      "end_time": 598130.0,
      "text": "and connected only by the image on a smartphone."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 598854.0,
      "end_time": 600589.0,
      "text": "Now I know this sounds like a dream,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 600613.0,
      "end_time": 603732.0,
      "text": "but in the lab we already have this working in mice,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 603756.0,
      "end_time": 605834.0,
      "text": "where it works better than existing methods"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 605859.0,
      "end_time": 609830.0,
      "text": "for the detection of lung, colon and ovarian cancer."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 610603.0,
      "end_time": 612837.0,
      "text": "And I hope that what this means"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 612861.0,
      "end_time": 618370.0,
      "text": "is that one day we can detect tumors in patients"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 618610.0,
      "end_time": 621354.0,
      "text": "sooner than 10 years after they&#39;ve started growing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 621378.0,
      "end_time": 623363.0,
      "text": "in all walks of life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 623387.0,
      "end_time": 625236.0,
      "text": "all around the globe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 625260.0,
      "end_time": 627995.0,
      "text": "and that this would lead to earlier treatments,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 628190.0,
      "end_time": 631617.0,
      "text": "and that we could save more lives than we can today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 631641.0,
      "end_time": 632925.0,
      "text": "with early detection."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 633686.0,
      "end_time": 634868.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 634892.0,
      "end_time": 642375.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}